{"id": "EUVD-2023-3295", "enisaUuid": "14e085b1-6ef0-3e31-b06f-3d717650b93b", "description": "yii2-authclient is an extension that adds OpenID, OAuth, OAuth2 and OpenId Connect consumers for the Yii framework 2.0. In yii2-authclient prior to version 2.2.15, the Oauth2 PKCE implementation is vulnerable in 2 ways. First, the `authCodeVerifier` should be removed after usage (similar to `authState`). Second, there is a risk for a `downgrade attack` if PKCE is being relied on for CSRF protection. Version 2.2.15 contains a patch for the issue. No known workarounds are available.", "datePublished": "2023-12-22T18:30:03", "dateUpdated": "2024-11-27T15:43:11", "baseScore": 6.8, "baseScoreVersion": "3.1", "baseScoreVector": "CVSS:3.1/AV:N/AC:H/PR:N/UI:R/S:U/C:H/I:H/A:N", "references": ["https://github.com/yiisoft/yii2-authclient/security/advisories/GHSA-rw54-6826-c8j5", "https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2023-50714", "https://github.com/yiisoft/yii2-authclient/commit/721ed974bc44137437b0cdc8454e137fff8db213", "https://github.com/yiisoft/yii2-authclient", "https://github.com/yiisoft/yii2-authclient/blob/0d1c3880f4d79e20aa1d77c012650b54e69695ff/src/OAuth1.php#L158", "https://github.com/yiisoft/yii2-authclient/blob/0d1c3880f4d79e20aa1d77c012650b54e69695ff/src/OAuth2.php#L121", "https://github.com/yiisoft/yii2-authclient/blob/0d1c3880f4d79e20aa1d77c012650b54e69695ff/src/OpenIdConnect.php#L420"], "aliases": ["CVE-2023-50714", "GHSA-rw54-6826-c8j5"], "assigner": "GitHub_M", "epss": 0.11, "enisaIdProduct": [{"id": "68223b3b-d118-32a2-920a-1e5e5b1a1952", "product": {"name": "yii2-authclient"}, "product_version": "< 2.2.15"}], "enisaIdVendor": [{"id": "50a64c5d-1131-3975-b55b-704ae91ae5ae", "vendor": {"name": "yiisoft"}}], "isExploited": false}